1. *Panduri* su priveli osumnjičenog za krađu. (The police officers arrested a suspect for theft.)
2. Videla sam kako *panduri* izvode nekoga iz zgrade. (I saw police officers escorting someone out of a building.)
3. Ulice su bile blokirane, a *panduri* su kontrolisali saobraćaj. (The streets were blocked and the police officers were controlling the traffic.)
4. *Panduri* su bili na visokom oprezu tokom velikog fudbalskog meča. (The police officers were on high alert during the big football match.)
5. *Panduri* su se pojavili nakon što smo prijavili buku u komšiluku. (The police officers showed up after we reported the noise in the neighborhood.)
6. Često se žale na *pandure* zbog zlostavljanja ovlašćenja. (People often complain about police officers abusing their authority.)
7. *Pandurima* je naređeno da ojačaju bezbednosne mere tokom festivala. (The police officers were ordered to strengthen security measures during the festival.)
8. Bio sam iznenađen kada sam video da je moj prijatelj postao *pandur*. (I was surprised when I saw that my friend became a police officer.)
9. Možete li mi pomoći da pronađem stanicu *pandura*? (Can you help me find the police station?)
10. U sudu je svedočio *pandur* koji je učestvovao u hapšenju. (A police officer who participated in the arrest testified in court.)